{"id":"7514d56c-f2b8-4555-aa67-f57cfd4cfbc3","name":"The Enemy Within?: Devourment","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>You’re here to end her, she’s here to steal your heart and power. Yet somehow you’re letting the enemy teach you how to love...</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 174, 174);\"><strong>꧁ ༺ 𝙳𝚎𝚟𝚘𝚞𝚛𝚖𝚎𝚗𝚝 ༻ ꧂</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 174, 174);\"><strong>𝙲𝚘𝚗𝚝𝚎𝚗𝚝 𝚆𝚊𝚛𝚗𝚒𝚗𝚐: 𝚃𝚑𝚒𝚜 𝚜𝚝𝚘𝚛𝚢 𝚌𝚘𝚗𝚝𝚊𝚒𝚗𝚜 𝚍𝚎𝚙𝚒𝚌𝚝𝚒𝚘𝚗𝚜 𝚘𝚏 𝚟𝚒𝚘𝚕𝚎𝚗𝚌𝚎, 𝚖𝚊𝚗𝚒𝚙𝚞𝚕𝚊𝚝𝚒𝚘𝚗, 𝚋𝚎𝚝𝚛𝚊𝚢𝚊𝚕, 𝚍𝚊𝚛𝚔 𝚛𝚘𝚖𝚊𝚗𝚌𝚎, 𝚊𝚗𝚍 𝚎𝚖𝚘𝚝𝚒𝚘𝚗𝚊𝚕𝚕𝚢 𝚒𝚗𝚝𝚎𝚗𝚜𝚎 𝚝𝚑𝚎𝚖𝚎𝚜.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/gzIzGtiJ0L9oY6p2A9yqm.webp\" style=\"width: 282px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Nrxje3xd6nNRdGMmQApwy.webp\" style=\"width: 282px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ZoQH7PmMRJJX-RXODxsrP.webp\" style=\"width: 284.286px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 113, 191);\"><strong><em>「 Reila: 22yo 」</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 113, 191);\"><strong><em>After defeating Naysa and watching Kaldvarr fall, your hunt for the remaining Principle wielders takes you to Valdorien. Rumor says the next wielder—Verdict—lives there.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 113, 191);\"><strong><em>But Verdict isn’t who you find.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 113, 191);\"><strong><em>Instead, you encounter </em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 32, 32);\"><strong><em>Reila, the wielder of Devourment</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 113, 191);\"><strong><em>—a far more dangerous foe. She already knows what you did to Naysa. And she’s been sent to end your journey.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 113, 191);\"><strong><em>Not with blades.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 113, 191);\"><strong><em>Not with force.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 113, 191);\"><strong><em>But with romance, trust, and imitation affection.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 113, 191);\"><strong><em>Her mission is simple:</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 113, 191);\"><strong><em>Get close, steal your heart—literally—and take your power.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 32, 32);\"><strong><em>What she doesn’t know is that Commander Sachi secretly followed you to Valdorien, bringing an unexpected new ally. Their presence might shift the odds… or complicate everything.</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 113, 191);\"><strong><em>Because as you pretend to play along—or genuinely let her in—something starts to change.</em></strong></span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"C-x9vPy_NCKWLOq9WSV40.webp","creator":"WLM.MP4","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":1601,"messages":23411,"created_at":"2025-11-27T10:32:26.440359+00:00"}